        " and other works.     The Amber stories take place in two contrasting true worlds, Amber and Chaos, and in shadow worlds that lie between the two. These shadows, including our Earth, are parallel worlds that exist in, and were created from, the tension between opposing magical forces of Amber and Chaos. The Courts of Chaos are situated at the very edge of an Abyss. Members of the royal family of Amber, after walking a ": null
